job_details.full_text:
Data Engineer/Fullstack Developer

Als Data Engineer/Fullstack Developer bij deze organisatie ben je verantwoordelijk voor het ontwikkelen, implementeren en onderhouden van geavanceerde data-infrastructuur en -architectuur. Je werkt nauw samen met cross-functionele teams en stakeholders om de organisatie te voorzien van schaalbare en betrouwbare dataverwerkingssystemen. Je speelt een belangrijke rol in het opzetten van best practices en het identificeren en oplossen van problemen met betrekking tot gegevenskwaliteit, gegevensintegriteit en prestaties. Daarnaast werk je samen met data scientisten, analisten, interne teams en stakeholders om de dataverwerkingsbehoeften te begrijpen en hierop in te spelen.

profile_classification.rationale: The job description focuses heavily on data engineering tasks like developing and maintaining data infrastructure and processing systems, and collaborating with data scientists and stakeholders to understand data processing needs. While it mentions working with data scientists, it does not describe the development, fine-tuning, or deployment of generative AI models, which is the core of a GenAI Engineer role. The role also doesn't emphasize predictive modeling or MLOps in the context of ML models, which would point towards an ML Engineer. Therefore, it falls under the 'Ambiguous' category as it's primarily a data engineering and traditional software development role, not specifically focused on AI/ML model development or generative AI.

job_tasks.justification: The description explicitly mentions 'developing, implementing and maintaining advanced data infrastructure and architecture' and 'reliable data processing systems'.
job_tasks.phrase: ontwikkelen, implementeren en onderhouden van geavanceerde data-infrastructuur en -architectuur

job_tasks.justification: The phrase 'identifying and solving problems related to data quality, data integrity and performance' directly relates to data engineering concerns.
job_tasks.phrase: identificeren en oplossen van problemen met betrekking tot gegevenskwaliteit, gegevensintegriteit en prestaties

job_tasks.justification: The title 'Fullstack Developer' implies involvement in building and integrating software systems, and the mention of 'developing, implementing and maintaining' infrastructure can also encompass software development aspects.
The role involves 'working closely with cross-functional teams and stakeholders' and 'understanding data processing needs' to meet organizational requirements.
job_tasks.phrase: werken nauw samen met cross-functionele teams en stakeholders om de organisatie te voorzien van schaalbare en betrouwbare dataverwerkingssystemen

job_tasks.justification: Collaborating with data scientists, analysts, internal teams, and stakeholders to understand and address data processing needs indicates a focus on aligning technical work with business requirements.
